  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  type 2 diabetes mellitus

          -  stable oral treatment with metfromin and/or sulfonylurea

          -  age 20 - 80 years

          -  angiographically confirmed atherosclerosis or hsCRP &gt; 1 mg/l

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  type 1 diabetes

          -  HbA1c &gt; 8.5 %

          -  severe disease

          -  acute coronary syndrome

          -  contraindications to pioglitazone (heart failure etc.)
      </textblock>
